      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne atinett tawa Swai-\ndita Waigu/ tawa Kalpa Dah-\nwida deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS irr Dah-\nwidam teefcham fwehrejs/ no ta\nwiſch ne nowehrsifees / es no\ntawas Meeſas Augteem eezel-\nschu us tawu Gohda-Krehflu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja tawi Behrni mannu\nDerribu turrehs,/ un mannu Lee-\nzibu/ ko es teem mahzischu/ tad\nir winnu Behrni us tawu Goh-\nda-Krehflu fehdehs muhscham.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS irr Zia-\nnu iſwehtejs / winnam turpatt\ngribbahs dſihwoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schi irr manna Duſfe-\nſchana muhschigi/ ſcheit dſihwo-\nschu es/ jo ta man gribbahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es fwehtischu winnas\nBarribu papillam/ un pa-ehti-\nnaschu winnas Nabbagus ar\nMaisi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un apgehrbschu winnas\nPreesterus ar Pestischannu / un\nwinnas Sweihtee ar leelu Ga-\nvileſchannu gawilehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tur likſchu es Dahwi-\ndam weenn Raggu usaugt/ es\nfmu ſawann Swaiditain weenn\nSpihdefli pataitijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winna Eenaidneeknu ap-\ngehrbschu es ar Kaunu/ bet pahr\nwinnu feedehs winna Krohnis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Angi/ rahda janke un\nRimihliga Leeta irr / kad\nBrahti weenprahtigi\nkohpa dſihwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas irr ta patt / ka ta\nwiſtlaubaka Etje / kas no Na-\nrona Galwas noteſk winna\nBahrdā/ kas noteſk lihds winna\nDrehbyn Wihlei.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Itt ka ta Rassa / kas no\nErmoza nokriht us Zianas Kal-\nneem/ jo tas KUNGS pafebla\ntur Sweihtibu un Dſihwoſchanu\nmuhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Angi/ Teizeet to KUN-\nGli wiſti Kalpi taKUN-\nGA / kas juhs Nakti\nta KUNGA Naminaſtahwat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pazelleet juhsas Rohkas\nprett to fwehtu Weetu/ un tei-\nzeet to KUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lai tas KUNGS tew\nfwehti no Zianas / kas Debbeſt\nun Semmi darrijs.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
